title: The Medieval Islamic Civilization - C. 6 (Art, Architectture 2)
description:
The Medieval Islamic Civilization - Collection 6 (Art, Architecture 2):

We have 14 titles here:

-  Contadini (Ed.) - Arab Painting; Text and Image in Illustrated Arabic Manuscripts (2007)

-  Du Ry - Art of Islam (1970)

-  Ekhtiar & Moore (Eds.) - Art of the Islamic World; a Resource for Educators (2012)

-  Grabar - The Formation of Islamic Art (1973)

-  Hess (Ed.) - The Arts of Fire; Islamic Influences on Glass and Ceramics of the Italian Renaissance (2004)

-  Hillenbrand - Islamic Art and Architecture (1999)

-  How to Recognize Islamic Art (1979)

-  Jenkins & Keene - Islamic Jewelry in the Metropolitan Museum of Art (1982)

-  Kadoi - Islamic Chinoiserie; the Art of Mongol Iran (2009)

-  Kavuri-Bauer - Monumental Matters; the Power, Subjectivity, and Space of India's Mughal Architecture (2011)

-  Migeon & Saladin - Art of Islam (2012)

-  Price - The Story of Moslem Art (1964)

-  Welch - The Emperors' Album; Images of Mughal India (1987)

-  Wilkinson - Nishapur; Some Early Islamic Buildings and Their Decoration (1986)
